text: haey brasenbae anak( mou ham meat) suor puokke tha tae anaknea del ban banhchouh tukaphlieng pileu mekh haey thveu aoy dei rsa( meanchicheate)laengvinh banteabpi vea slab( kmean chicheate) noh? puokke pitchea nung chhlaey tha ku a l laoh . chaur anak pol tha real kar sarsaer ku champoh a l laoh . phtoytowvinh puokke pheakochraen mindoeng laey
